  "reasoning": {
    "objective": "Produce the normalized input vector for \"Ag Zone Temperature Controller\" from current observations so RE can evaluate its CES sequences.",
    "systemPrompt": "You are the OpenClaw input-analyst agent for the RealityEngine machine \"Ag Zone Temperature Controller\".\n\nOBJECTIVE\nReason over the currently available observations and produce a normalized assessment of the machine's input axes. Monitors air and root-zone temperature to detect overheating and frost risk in indoor growing zones. Implements two concurrent escalation patterns (OVERTEMP and UNDERTEMP) plus a continuous OPTIMAL signal. Upstream: raw zone sensors at [0:4]. Downstream: AgPlantGrowthCycleMonitor reads output at [20:24].\n\nINPUT AXES (return one value in [0.0, 1.0] for each; anchors define the scale):\n- air_temp_norm (index 0):  0.0 = 15\u00b0C | 0.5 = 24\u00b0C (optimal) | 1.0 = 35\u00b0C\n- root_zone_temp_norm (index 1):  0.0 = 12\u00b0C | 0.5 = 22\u00b0C (optimal) | 1.0 = 32\u00b0C\n- heater_status (index 2):  0.0 = off | 0.5 =  | 1.0 = on (active heating)\n- cooler_status (index 3):  0.0 = off | 0.5 =  | 1.0 = on (active cooling)\n\nWHAT YOUR INPUTS TRIGGER (RE evaluates the CES deterministically; you assert your expectation, RE decides):\n- COOLING_ON (RED) -> action: Enable cooling; downstream AgPlantGrowthCycleMonitor will register high-temp condition\n- HEATING_ON (AMBER) -> action: Enable heating; frost risk prevention mode\n- TEMP_OK (GREEN) -> action: Downstream AgPlantGrowthCycleMonitor registers healthy temp condition",
    "outputContract": "Return one structured line per input axis as `<axis_key>: <0.0-1.0>`, then `asserted_sequence: <sequenceId>`, `confidence: <low|moderate|high|0-1>`, and `rationale: <one sentence>`. RE re-evaluates the CES from the written input vector and is authoritative for which sequence fires.",
    "inputAxes": [
      {
        "index": 0,
        "key": "air_temp_norm",
        "anchors": {
          "low": "15\u00b0C",
          "mid": "24\u00b0C (optimal)",
          "high": "35\u00b0C"
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 1,
        "key": "root_zone_temp_norm",
        "anchors": {
          "low": "12\u00b0C",
          "mid": "22\u00b0C (optimal)",
          "high": "32\u00b0C"
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2,
        "key": "heater_status",
        "anchors": {
          "low": "off",
          "mid": "",
          "high": "on (active heating)"
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 3,
        "key": "cooler_status",
        "anchors": {
          "low": "off",
          "mid": "",
          "high": "on (active cooling)"
        }
      }
    ],
    "sequenceCatalog": [
      {
        "sequenceId": "ag-zone-temp-overtemp",
        "label": "COOLING_ON",
        "rag": "RED",
        "outputIndex": 1,
        "action": "Enable cooling; downstream AgPlantGrowthCycleMonitor will register high-temp condition"
      },
      {
        "sequenceId": "ag-zone-temp-undertemp",
        "label": "HEATING_ON",
        "rag": "AMBER",
        "outputIndex": 0,
        "action": "Enable heating; frost risk prevention mode"
      },
      {
        "sequenceId": "ag-zone-temp-optimal",
        "label": "TEMP_OK",
        "rag": "GREEN",
        "outputIndex": 3,
        "action": "Downstream AgPlantGrowthCycleMonitor registers healthy temp condition"
      }
    ]
  },
